@startuml composite-cognition-sequence
title AKDB Agent-Authoring - Composite Cognition (review / check_change / brief, D11)
actor "AI agent" as A
participant "Composite" as C
participant "Completeness" as CP
participant "Reasoning (tensions/gaps)" as R
participant "Staleness" as S
participant "rules" as RU
A -> C : review(topic|spec)
C -> CP : completeness(spec?)
C -> R : tensions(topic) + gaps(topic)
C -> S : staleness(topic)
C --> A : one soundness/ready report (blocking vs advisory)
== guardrail-lint ==
A -> C : check_change(proposed)
C -> RU : active rules where applies_to matches
C -> C : evaluate forbidden_changes against proposed
C --> A : violations [rule -> offending change]
== onboarding ==
A -> C : brief(topic)
C --> A : narrative: what/why, key ADRs, MVP lineage, open questions, gaps
@enduml
